<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7915392>
    dc:description "Figs 82–88. Terminalia (♂) of Stylogaster hauseri sp. n. (holotype): (82) surstylus, lateral view; (83) same, dorsal view; (84) cercus, lateral view; (85) same, dorsal view; (86) phallus sheath of hypandrium, lateral view; (87) phallus; (88) sperm pump and ejaculatory apodeme. Abbreviations: ce – cercus; hys – phallus sheath of hypandrium; su – surstylus. Not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7915392/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7915394>
